Review: To be honest I kinda felt reminded of my family, we don’t really play games, we just wanna kill each other.
They made the new evil Captain America guy get attacked by dirty pool water. Then they attacked the audience with the worst CGI imaginable.
They sure delivered on the title!

Movie: Captain Underpants: The First Epic Movie
Review: If we’re being completely honest with ourselves it’s crazy to think Captain Underpants isn’t valued the same way Shrek is at Dreamworks.
I don’t hate it because it aged poorly, I hate it because it’s not funny.
There are approximately 64 uses of Noodle (62 verbal, 2 written) and 19 uses of Willy (all verbal) in 2023’s Wonka.
If you combined Cocomelon, TikTok and heroine they would merge into this movie.
No better way to start Christmas than with a cup of joe and the best damn action-drama film ever created.

Holy shit.From the moment Zac Efron hit a crossbody off the top rope I was entranced. What an electrifying and beautiful film that not only pays respect to the sport of wrestling but also one of the most famous families to ever enter the squared circle.It’s mind-boggling how there isn’t even a conversation around this film for awards. The level of technicality and subtly from Efron, White, Dickinson, and Simons is wondrous. Their physicality and ring work is…
